<p>It is a goal of all residents of a state to improve the knowledge of adolescents about reproductive health, encourage positive and healthy responses and attitudes towards sexuality, delay the onset of participation in sexual acts for adolescents, decrease the possibility of risky behavior among those adolescents that are already active and provide areas that are youth-friendly, where trained personnel and peer educators can be accessed by these youths. </p>
<p>Guard the sexual and reproductive health rights of adolescents for a better future. Educate adolescents on their sexuality. More knowledge is power. Ignorance is also no defense. </p>
